      <JapaneseText>エターナルソードは使わせねぇ。
デュークを止めるぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We can't let him use the Eternal Sword.
We've gotta stop Duke.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やろう、リッド！
デュークにわからせてあげなきゃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's do this, Reid!
We've gotta make Duke understand.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>この世界は、滅ぼさなきゃいけない程
ひどいものじゃないって！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This world isn't so terrible
that it needs to be destroyed!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
